g.text: Configure logging for all of smol-k8s-lab.
Save app credentials to a local password manager vault. Only Bitwarden
is supported at this time, but if enabled, Bitwarden can be used as
your k8s external secret provider. To avoid a password prompt, export
the following env vars: BW_PASSWORD, BW_CLIENTID, BW_CLIENTSECRET
If window behavior is set to same window, command runs
